headline.print_headline: Ukrainians in Canada Send Money, Shed Tears for Kiev
headline.main: Ukrainians in Canada Send Money, Shed Tears for Kiev

lead_paragraph: The small gilded chapel at the Ukrainian Canadian Care Center, a retirement residence in suburban Toronto, is usually shuttered and dark midweek. But on Thursday, dozens of elderly immigrants and their caregivers gathered to pray for protesters and family back in Kiev.
